### ─── 1. REGISTRATION FLOW ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Step A: Register (Saves to Pending)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "role": "student"
}

### Step B: Verify Email (Saves to Users table)
# Note: Check your real email for the 6-digit OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "otp": "{{otp}}"
}

### ─── 2. AUTHENTICATION ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login
# This sets the 'refresh_token' cookie automatically
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Get My Profile
# Copy 'access_token' from Login response and paste into @authToken at the top
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Refresh Access Token
# Requires 'refresh_token' cookie
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── 3. LOGOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Logout (This Device Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Logout (ALL Devices)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── 4. PASSWORD RECOVERY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Forgot Password (Sends OTP to email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### Reset Password
# Note: Check your email for the new OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "otp": "{{otp}}",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### ─── 5. USER MANAGEMENT (Internal/Testing) ────────────────────────────────

### Find All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### Find One User
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### Update User
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

### Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1
